                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18120916-21-off117 t18120916-21-cd118"></join>, six penny-pieces, and one hundred and eight halfpence, the property of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18120916-21-victim250" type="victimName">
